  "texts": [
    "However, many models rely on data from the internet, which feature a wide range of accuracy levels.",
    "Both Gen AI and analytical AI models also are probabilistic rather than deterministic.",
    "Thus, analytical AI models sometimes make incorrect predictions about whether a person will repay a loan or buy a product at a particular price.",
    "Similarly, Gen AI models have a well-known tendency to \"hallucinate,\" or create inaccurate output (Vana et al., 2024).",
    "As Huang and Rust (2024) acknowledge, Gen AI is good at recognizing expressed emotions but may be prone to hallucinating responses."
  ],
